#

Orange Creamsicle Popsicles

250 min
$5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-FreeVegan

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Dessert

Tags:

DessertSummerFrozen Treat

Description

Cool off with these creamy and refreshing orange popsicles, perfect for a hot day!

Ingredients

  • fresh orange juice: 2 cups
  • coconut milk: 1 cup
  • honey or maple syrup: 1/4 cup
  • orange zest: 1 tablespoon
  • vanilla extract: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: a pinch
